{"tid":844958,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度男不滿好友想睡媽媽 斬首對方且拎頭上街","createTime":"2018-10-02T09:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T09:52:29.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ef380f2800c96fe054016b82cd98e44d3a342d31","tid":844958,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/173933_012645422dc8be4ee7c0586485ccd244.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F173933_012645422dc8be4ee7c0586485ccd244.png&h=761ba3da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印度卡納塔克邦（Karnataka）一名24歲男子帕雪帕提（Pashupati）近年不滿35歲的兒時好友吉里許（Girish）對自己媽媽心懷邪念，上月底時在一處村莊持刀將他「斬首」，且騎車提著死者鮮血直流的頭到警局自首。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，吉里許自3年前開始，就對帕雪帕提媽媽有意思，且多次想與她發生性關係，因此兩人經常起爭執，友情日益降溫。據悉，他們兩人居住的村莊村長曾介入調解，但因村長僅警告吉里許不許再對帕雪帕提媽媽有非分之想外，並無祭出其他懲處，讓帕雪帕提無法接受才萌生「斬首」計畫。<br />\n<br />\n上月29日，帕雪帕提先向吉里許稱已原諒對方，並邀他到家裡坐坐，吉里許受邀後，帕雪帕提還提供茶水降低吉里許戒心；相談不久，帕雪帕提提議要騎車載吉里許出門晃晃，於是吉里許不假思索地也答應。待帕雪帕提騎到一處村莊的偏僻地帶時，兩人又因同件事發生激烈爭吵，這時帕雪帕提便持刀斬首吉里許。<br />\n<br />\n事發後，帕雪帕提拎著吉里許血淋淋的人頭，騎20公里的車回市中心的警察局自首；警方指出，死者應是在當天早上遇害，全案仍在偵辦中。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，此事是該邦9月發生的第3起斬首事件，其中一次是在9月11日，一名丈夫懷疑妻子外遇而將她斬首，且也把她的人頭提到警察局自首。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2567812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2567812&d=kQFAM6terdWJr1P%2FpqNKgDM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=b3b5d214\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2567812&h=031e9f06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2567812</a>"},{"pid":"839dfd506d71f1cbf400c82951af3bf36f8c573e","tid":844958,"uid":100230,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:42:24.000Z","msg":"你估屌人老母唔駛代價呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b34c281e236cc3fd9cb23ffca127c969de9de8","tid":844958,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:42:33.000Z","msg":"屌我老母?! 斬死你"},{"pid":"2e543a641344a52e5db2537a5c8de2fd2ecb6e44","tid":844958,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:43:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1bcbdf6af07380d3dcdf2695d77b1fe71259cd2","tid":844958,"uid":48942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:43:37.000Z","msg":"你估屌人老母唔洗付出代價呀？"},{"pid":"1bfa496816b4b06abb1f4e0ce02aeee0708714dc","tid":844958,"uid":41349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:44:12.000Z","msg":"究竟會有幾多連登仔會俾人斬首<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700ffe313341e912cfa1dbb628d6a277984c8bed","tid":844958,"uid":121130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:45:10.000Z","msg":"以後唔講屌你老母 我錯"},{"pid":"f354f8f145e1c3ba0e4e23dfdc734134b0d93ddd","tid":844958,"uid":445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:52:29.000Z","msg":"有日故友曰 ：吾想與令堂敦睦夫婦之倫"}]}